Property Brothers at Home - Season 3, Episode 3 (Drew's Honeymoon House)




A Room for Romance

Jonathan continues helping Drew and his fiancee renovate their vintage Los Angeles fixer-upper. With just 12 weeks to totally transform the house before the big pre-wedding party, the brothers give the master bedroom and bathroom a makeover with a touch of old Hollywood glamour. In the end, the happy couple realizes their dreams of Drew having a walk-in closet of his own and Linda getting a room dedicated to her crafting passion.




Original Air Date: 06-Dec-2017
